{"tid":2452423,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"當上帝閂左你一對門既時候，會唔會開返另一對門俾你？","createTime":"2021-03-18T23:22:11.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-18T23:55:22.000Z","uid":340729,"like":12,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"aa7079f0454379f10fcc17667bd0384793193ff7","tid":2452423,"uid":340729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T23:22:11.000Z","msg":"自小我就樣衰＋細粒，中學溝女個時，條女都叫我去絕育，自此都無曬心機做人。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n考完dse之後，淨係可以報HKU MBBS，好唔情願之下入左。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n過幾年實習之後識左個教授，時間長左之後同佢做左sp．<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n去到宜家，去做政府醫院做，一日做十幾個鐘，然後人工得幾十皮左右，做到隻狗咁。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n試問一個男人追唔到女，讀唔成書，日日做打工仔，人生有咩意義？<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />上帝閂左一對門會順手閂多兩對門，最後落埋閘<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />上帝會開對木門對竹門俾你"},{"pid":"3696af6f90c10e9786a278faa2f2b67ba5f0f2b1","tid":2452423,"uid":90323,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T23:23:48.000Z","msg":"其實唔駛咁想做有錢人， 無乜特別。"},{"pid":"09ee017a0ab232f2e00180601a88c504a0413be0","tid":2452423,"uid":132446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T23:25:49.000Z","msg":"政府醫院做，一日做十幾個鐘，然後人工得幾十皮左右<br />\n<br />\n年薪?"},{"pid":"97b7a6e091e3205491259aace724042e25d43f2d","tid":2452423,"uid":340729,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3696af6f90c10e9786a278faa2f2b67ba5f0f2b1","tid":2452423,"uid":90323,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T23:23:48.000Z","msg":"其實唔駛咁想做有錢人， 無乜特別。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T23:26:39.000Z","msg":"其實每日可以食下唔同餐廳<br />\n唔憂米<br />\n消費大約200蚊到已經好開心"},{"pid":"077335077699a9dd9975537281f1f16a5a458655","tid":2452423,"uid":69650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T23:27:24.000Z","msg":"有sp喎"},{"pid":"d2a654fe4b0141a9661d1da2c5e84e57843ab4d3","tid":2452423,"uid":25560,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T23:28:04.000Z","msg":"樓主係男，教授又係男？"},{"pid":"42e992696e47611f257fa2be167b450b3a1df00e","tid":2452423,"uid":58147,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T23:28:27.000Z","msg":"我人生只有牆，冇任何門俾我選擇。"},{"pid":"3d06df50161e739e4a1945cbafcab484b93e1c29","tid":2452423,"uid":340729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"09ee017a0ab232f2e00180601a88c504a0413be0","tid":2452423,"uid":132446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T23:25:49.000Z","msg":"政府醫院做，一日做十幾個鐘，然後人工得幾十皮左右<br />\n<br />\n年薪?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T23:28:28.000Z","msg":"係呀，差十幾年先可以上到半山。<br />\n最近同個sp Professor夾緊錢"},{"pid":"1e22846d1dbd5690af31b6f13c7ec104c3d469bf","tid":2452423,"uid":340729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d2a654fe4b0141a9661d1da2c5e84e57843ab4d3","tid":2452423,"uid":25560,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T23:28:04.000Z","msg":"樓主係男，教授又係男？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T23:29:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23dfd5905a44b607aed7efc4d327de5ded58137b","tid":2452423,"uid":385793,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d2a654fe4b0141a9661d1da2c5e84e57843ab4d3","tid":2452423,"uid":25560,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T23:28:04.000Z","msg":"樓主係男，教授又係男？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T23:31:25.000Z","msg":"this"},{"pid":"4e4efadc089d9c4f4a506f17a8df52e83a58daee","tid":2452423,"uid":142097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T23:33:12.000Z","msg":"巴打加油，遲d 有錢要條女奶到雪雪聲"},{"pid":"9dba8f1432d501c1f344fc779b46a09ff6c0b4b2"